                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1004799553" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1004799553" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1004799553">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/nina1104/">slowlife大小姐</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-01-27</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">一直想要有一年要在读书计划里写上：今年要看《追忆似水年华》。但每一年都因为没有把握有如此长的时间或者一直借不到第一卷而作罢。结果先看了这一本。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

